716
00:38:13,312 --> 00:38:15,843
♪ Ah ah ah ah ah ♪

717
00:38:15,848 --> 00:38:17,845
♪ Ah ah ah ah ah ♪

718
00:38:17,850 --> 00:38:20,447
♪ I'm comin' for you ♪

719
00:38:20,452 --> 00:38:22,116
♪ You can feel it ♪

